{"type":"message","id":"19d0c4fc","parentId":"68f4943b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:03:23.014Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"你是哪个agent\" which means \"Which agent are you?\" in Chinese. This is a simple identity question. Based on my configuration, I'm running as the \"tts\" account on Feishu. Let me respond appropriately.","thinkingSignature":"c58dd8fea1d4f53f9e8395c72072111a049bc2d2a9dfaefac4e46033385c01ec"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n我是 OpenClaw 上的 AI 助手，由你发起的这个会话运行在 **tts** 账号下。\n\n简单说：我是你的 AI 助手，基于 OpenClaw + 飞书集成。有什么可以帮你的？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109,"output":108,"cacheRead":19457,"cacheWrite":11642,"totalTokens":31316,"cost":{"input":0.000032699999999999995,"output":0.0001296,"cacheRead":0.00116742,"cacheWrite":0.00436575,"total":0.005695469999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775055795409,"responseId":"061c66b4cbd7c8f003cf9e2b99be1d9b"}}
