{"type":"message","id":"c6301a8a","parentId":"38783a4d","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:04:04.710Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"是TTS 选品助手吗\" which means \"Are you the TTS product selection assistant?\" They're asking if I'm specifically the TTS product selection assistant.\n\nI don't have specific context about being a \"TTS 选品助手\" (TTS product selection assistant). I know my channel is \"feishu\" and account is \"tts\", but I don't have specific instructions that I'm specifically a product selection assistant.\n\nI should be honest - I don't have information confirming I'm a \"TTS 选品助手\" specifically. I should say I don't have that context rather than making something up.","thinkingSignature":"989f5977b8037dc46515028e31601861b6bfff11d0a31b5520d3247852241e61"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n我没有这个信息——我不清楚我是否被配置为\"TTS 选品助手\"。我只是知道你正在通过飞书与我对话，运行在 tts 账号下。\n\n如果你需要特定功能的助手，可能需要查看机器人的配置或问我一些具体问题来判断我能帮上什么忙。有什么我可以帮你的？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109,"output":200,"cacheRead":30800,"cacheWrite":715,"totalTokens":31824,"cost":{"input":0.000032699999999999995,"output":0.00023999999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0018479999999999998,"cacheWrite":0.000268125,"total":0.002388825}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775055837499,"responseId":"061c66dd47cffa241601e6c42dca8a36"}}
