{"type":"message","id":"f1e3c943","parentId":"521edaa1","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:05:37.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"你是主agent的\" which means \"You belong to the main agent\" or \"You're the main agent's...\" - seems like they're asking if I'm a sub-agent or the main agent. They might be trying to figure out if they're talking to the primary AI or a subordinate one.\n\nGiven the context, I should clarify my role - I'm the main AI assistant in this conversation, not a sub-agent spawned by another agent.","thinkingSignature":"661e8d2511535352e67eb97b336ae880a1f5ff2e2bf1e6740dcb117beb03ce78"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n是的，我就是这个对话里的主 agent，直接为你服务。有什么需要帮忙的？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109,"output":116,"cacheRead":31207,"cacheWrite":812,"totalTokens":32244,"cost":{"input":0.000032699999999999995,"output":0.0001392,"cacheRead":0.0018724199999999999,"cacheWrite":0.00030450000000000003,"total":0.0023488199999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775055931803,"responseId":"061c673ca298b600c4bc5ebefce2d65a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3da4231","parentId":"f1e3c943","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:06:24.769Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-01 23:06:23 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b53e7083f08a0c3dac204ac3c2ab]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53e7083f08a0c3dac204ac3c2ab\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-01 23:06 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n啥意思呀， 我是用这个绑定到 后台 tts选品助手agent 上，  主agent一直在 kiit这个机器人上"}],"timestamp":1775055984760}}
{"type":"message","id":"24337c93","parentId":"e3da4231","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:06:33.664Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is explaining that they use this to bind to the backend TTS product selection assistant agent, and the main agent is always on a robot called \"kiit\". They're clarifying the architecture - they have:\n1. A Feishu account (tts) that's bound to a backend \"TTS选品助手agent\"\n2. The main agent runs on \"kiit\" robot\n\nSo they're saying this tts Feishu account is connected to a product selection sub-agent, not the main agent which lives on kiit. They're correcting my understanding.\n\nThis is helpful context - it explains the architecture. The user seems to be explaining how things are set up, perhaps because they were confused by my earlier responses.","thinkingSignature":"9e6605dd997f61e1968e958b63eb44b3be4a3b247979052baaea01ac69da027e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n<final>\n哦明白了！谢谢解释。所以架构是这样的：\n\n- **kiit** 机器人 → 运行主 agent\n- **tts** 飞书账号 → 绑定到后台的\"TTS选品助手\" sub-agent\n\n而我（这次对话）是通过 tts 账号过来的，所以应该是那个选品助手 sub-agent，不是主 agent。\n\n那你找我是因为选品相关的问题吗？😊\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109,"output":235,"cacheRead":31715,"cacheWrite":750,"totalTokens":32809,"cost":{"input":0.000032699999999999995,"output":0.00028199999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0019029,"cacheWrite":0.00028125000000000003,"total":0.0024988499999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775055984764,"responseId":"061c677119043a6df107caf35f4e7450"}}
