{"type":"message","id":"143fb62d","parentId":"de5c896f","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:07:39.068Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"你说的是对的，我要让你绑定回去\" - \"You're right, I want to switch you back\" or \"I want to bind you back to the main agent\". \n\nSo they want to go back to talking to the main agent on the kiit robot, not this TTS product selection sub-agent. This seems like a configuration issue on their end - they accidentally ended up in this sub-agent session when they wanted to be in the main agent session.\n\nI should acknowledge what they want and let them know they'll need to go back to the kiit robot to talk to the main agent, or guide them on how to switch back.","thinkingSignature":"cb05733a33a40b03198d23f84b1143e9d83d0667c4d9a015457a94200a3e6886"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n明白，你是说现在这个 tts 账号绑定的选品助手 sub-agent 不是你想聊的那个，你想切回 kiit 机器人上的主 agent。\n\n这个应该是 OpenClaw 里的会话路由配置问题——你在 kiit 那边重新发起对话应该就能回到主 agent 了。\n\n需要我帮你排查一下路由配置吗？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109,"output":209,"cacheRead":32135,"cacheWrite":875,"totalTokens":33328,"cost":{"input":0.000032699999999999995,"output":0.00025079999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0019280999999999999,"cacheWrite":0.000328125,"total":0.0025397249999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775056051608,"responseId":"061c67b4c9b3d92fb8081d8224f5269b"}}
