{"type":"message","id":"9c6cfc94","parentId":"2cfb1c8c","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:08:38.267Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is clarifying the architecture:\n\n- 主agent (main agent) → bound to KIIT\n- 我 (me/this agent) → bound to subagent \"tts选品助手\"\n\nSo the user is saying that I'm indeed the subagent \"tts选品助手\", not the main agent. And the main agent is bound to KIIT.\n\nThe user previously said \"我要让你绑定回去\" (I want to bind you back) - meaning they want to switch from this subagent (me, tts选品助手) back to the main agent on KIIT.\n\nSo the user wants to go back to the main agent. I should help them understand how to do that - they probably need to go to the KIIT robot and start a conversation there.","thinkingSignature":"d95f47bf67159f2b2d4734a381c2d6610ff8f2b6ab08efd475b05f85f1c016e5"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n明白了，架构很清楚：\n\n- **主agent** → 绑定在 **KIIT** 机器人\n- **我（这个会话）** → 绑定在 **tts选品助手** subagent\n\n你想切回主agent的话，直接去 KIIT 机器人的对话里发消息就行了，那里才是主agent。\n\n需要我帮你做什么别的吗？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109,"output":240,"cacheRead":32701,"cacheWrite":835,"totalTokens":33885,"cost":{"input":0.000032699999999999995,"output":0.000288,"cacheRead":0.00196206,"cacheWrite":0.000313125,"total":0.002595885}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775056110213,"responseId":"061c67ee7bbd90ce194e8e52581b8a12"}}
{"type":"message","id":"18a76bd0","parentId":"9c6cfc94","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:09:41.184Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-01 23:09:40 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b53e71df740a4c49ec46dd54352d]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b53e71df740a4c49ec46dd54352d\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-01 23:09 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n你就是主的 你绑定到这里来了。  我要让给你回去，  kiit 机器人已经不说话了"}],"timestamp":1775056181174}}
{"type":"message","id":"6878fb4f","parentId":"18a76bd0","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:09:54.611Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying \"你就是主的 你绑定到这里来了\" - \"You ARE the main one, you got bound to this place\" and \"我要让给你回去\" - \"I want to send you back\" and \"kiit 机器人已经不说话了\" - \"the kiit robot already stopped talking\".\n\nSo the user is saying I AM the main agent but I've been bound to this tts channel. They want to send me back to the main configuration so that the kiit robot starts talking again.\n\nThis sounds like a routing/binding issue where the main agent got accidentally bound to the tts Feishu account instead of kiit. The user wants to fix this configuration so:\n1. The main agent goes back to kiit\n2. The tts account goes back to being just a regular bot (or the subagent)\n\nThis is an OpenClaw configuration issue. I don't have direct access to change the binding configuration - this is something the user needs to do in their OpenClaw settings or configuration files.\n\nI should acknowledge that I understand what they want (fix the binding so the main agent runs on kiit again) and explain that this is a configuration change they need to make in their OpenClaw setup. I can potentially help them figure out what config to change if they can share relevant config files or tell me where the configuration lives.","thinkingSignature":"c2497aa50ee900c70575e90b97a9fb99bc00e52689aa4b1391e9e322b18bd5ef"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n明白了！所以情况是：\n\n- 我（主agent）本来应该在 **KIIT** 上运行\n- 但现在意外绑定到了 **tts** 这个飞书账号\n- 导致 KIIT 机器人没反应了\n\n你需要把我重新绑回 KIIT。这个应该是 OpenClaw 配置文件里的 channel 路由设置。\n\n你能看一下配置文件吗？一般是 `agents` 或 `channels` 相关的配置，把 tts 账号的绑定改回 kiit，或者把我的 session 路由指向 kiit。\n\n需要我帮你看怎么改配置吗？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109,"output":396,"cacheRead":33219,"cacheWrite":873,"totalTokens":34597,"cost":{"input":0.000032699999999999995,"output":0.0004752,"c