{"type":"message","id":"b87a1ff0","parentId":"7580361f","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:17:59.032Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the actual configuration! The user has shared the agent configuration:\n\n- **main** agent: Default agent, workspace at `~/.openclaw/workspace`, model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7, routing: default (no explicit rules)\n- **tts** agent (TTS-选品专家): Workspace at `~/.openclaw/workspace-selector`, routing: Feishu tts\n\nSo the main agent is at `~/.openclaw/workspace` and the tts subagent is at `~/.openclaw/workspace-selector`.\n\nThe user said the main agent should be bound to KIIT but it's currently... wait, the routing shows \"Feishu tts\" for the tts agent, and the main agent has \"routing: default (no explicit rules)\". \n\nThe issue is probably in the channel bindings. The user said they want to send me (the main agent) back to KIIT. The tts account is currently bound to the tts subagent.\n\nLet me ask the user what specific binding needs to change, or what the KIIT channel is. The configuration shows the agents but I need to understand what \"KIIT\" refers to in terms of the channel configuration.\n\nActually, the user originally said:\n- 主agent main绑定到 KIIT 上\n- 我 (this agent) 绑定到 subagent tts选品助手\n\nBut now I can see from the config:\n- main agent has routing: default (no explicit rules)\n- tts agent has routing: Feishu tts\n\nSo the tts channel is bound to the tts subagent. But where is KIIT? Maybe KIIT is another channel that should be bound to main?\n\nI should ask the user what they want to change - do they want the main agent to be accessible via KIIT channel? Or do they want to change the routing so that when someone messages via the KIIT channel, they get the main agent instead?\n\n\nBased on what the user said about KIIT becoming unresponsive while I'm responding here instead, it sounds like they want the routing adjusted so the main agent handles the KIIT channel instead of the tts subagent.","thinkingSignature":"638ce3cff39ebffd49a07af7ebc865f77de58c81feb1356865d4ba1d734b0426"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！现在能看到配置了：\n\n- **main** agent → workspace: `~/.openclaw/workspace`，routing: default\n- **tts** (TTS-选品专家) → workspace: `~/.openclaw/workspace-selector`，routing: Feishu tts\n\n所以问题是：**tts 这个飞书账号** 绑定到了 `tts` subagent，而 **main agent** 没有明确的路由规则。\n\n你说的 **KIIT** 是另一个飞书机器人吗？还是说 KIIT 应该是绑定到 main agent 的？\n\n你希望怎么调整？\n\n1. 让 **KIIT** 绑定到 **main** agent？\n2. 还是让 **tts** 账号重新绑定到 **main** agent？\n\n告诉我你想要的结果，我帮你改配置。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109,"output":608,"cacheRead":44074,"cacheWrite":2339,"totalTokens":47130,"cost":{"input":0.000032699999999999995,"output":0.0007296,"cacheRead":0.0026444399999999996,"cacheWrite":0.000877125,"total":0.0042838649999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775056657307,"responseId":"061c6a118a8dd86e1acb26f33d9c11d1"}}
