{"type":"message","id":"0390b04f","parentId":"c523df4b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:28:38.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to list the available skills. I should show them the skills that are installed in the OpenClaw workspace. Looking at the available_skills from earlier, there are many skills listed. Let me provide the list.","thinkingSignature":"a10dfec6381a975722114b6580115446320dc70829644586818855101d549985"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n当前可用的 Skills：\n\n**飞书相关：**\n- feishu-bitable - 飞书多维表格管理\n- feishu-calendar - 飞书日历与日程管理\n- feishu-channel-rules - Lark 频道输出规则\n- feishu-create-doc - 创建飞书云文档\n- feishu-fetch-doc - 获取飞书云文档内容\n- feishu-im-read - 飞书 IM 消息读取工具\n- feishu-task - 飞书任务管理\n- feishu-troubleshoot - 飞书插件问题排查\n- feishu-update-doc - 更新飞书云文档\n\n**OpenClaw 相关：**\n- clawflow - 工作流管理\n- clawflow-inbox-triage - 收件箱分类流程\n- clawhub - 搜索/安装/发布 skill\n- coding-agent - 编码任务代理（Codex/Claude Code）\n- gemini - Gemini CLI\n- healthcheck - 主机安全检查\n- node-connect - 节点连接诊断\n- openclaw-doctor - OpenClaw 诊断与维修\n- skill-creator - 创建/编辑/改进 AgentSkills\n- vibesurf - 浏览器自动化\n\n**其他：**\n- weather - 天气查询\n\n你想用哪个 skill？或者你想问的是 KIIT 相关的问题？\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109,"output":335,"cacheRead":51302,"cacheWrite":1047,"totalTokens":52793,"cost":{"input":0.000032699999999999995,"output":0.00040199999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0030781199999999997,"cacheWrite":0.000392625,"total":0.003905445}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775057309208,"responseId":"061c6c9df6f3194517f815b635e5ee31"}}
