{"type":"message","id":"4b78b588","parentId":"c302679c","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:36:03.965Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is frustrated and saying \"搞什么呀\" which is like \"What are you doing?\" or \"What's going on?\". They're clearly getting impatient with all the approval requests. \n\nLet me just summarize what we found and give them a clear next step. The key finding is that `openclaw agents` has commands for `bind` and `bindings` to manage routing. \n\nFrom the help output:\n- `openclaw agents add` - Add a new isolated agent\n- `openclaw agents bind` - Add routing bindings for an agent\n- `openclaw agents bindings` - List routing bindings\n- `openclaw agents delete` - Delete an agent and prune workspace/state\n- `openclaw agents list` - List configured agents\n- `openclaw agents set-identity` - Update an agent identity\n- `openclaw agents unbind` - Remove routing bindings\n\nSo to fix the KIIT binding issue, we need to:\n1. First run `openclaw agents bindings list` to see current bindings\n2. Then use `openclaw agents bind <agent> <channel>` to bind KIIT to main\n\nLet me just give them the commands they need to run themselves since I'm having approval issues.","thinkingSignature":"a16403b544c7a5530dee3a08144200cb7a3024b1200c0c36ccc60294a58798ce"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉让你烦了！😓\n\n我找到了关键命令。你自己运行这几个命令就行：\n\n**查看当前所有绑定：**\n```\nopenclaw agents bindings list\n```\n\n**把 KIIT 绑定到 main agent：**\n```\nopenclaw agents bind main <KIIT的channel名字>\n```\n\n**查看所有 channels（确认 KIIT 的名字）：**\n```\nopenclaw channels list\n```\n\n你先跑 `openclaw agents bindings list` 看看现在有哪些绑定，把结果发给我，我帮你确定下一步怎么改。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109,"output":354,"cacheRead":58598,"cacheWrite":1179,"totalTokens":60240,"cost":{"input":0.000032699999999999995,"output":0.00042479999999999997,"cacheRead":0.00351588,"cacheWrite":0.000442125,"total":0.004415504999999999}},"stopReason":"stop",