{"type":"message","id":"97e224ad","parentId":"8a7d22d0","timestamp":"2026-04-01T15:37:01.511Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said `openclaw agents bindings list` is not correct. Let me think - the help output showed:\n\n```\nCommands: add Add a new isolated agent bind Add routing bindings for an agent bindings List routing bindings delete Delete an agent and prune workspace/state list List configured agents set-identity Update an agent identity (name/theme/emoji/avatar) unbind Remove routing bindings for an agent\n```\n\nSo it looks like `bindings` is a command itself, not a subcommand of `agents`. So the command might be:\n- `openclaw agents bindings` (without `list`) to list bindings\n\nOr maybe:\n- `openclaw bindings list`\n\nLet me suggest trying `openclaw agents bindings` alone, or check help again.","thinkingSignature":"1bea9cbfe2a6daeff909712aae7bf0c1d9ef8d7de0c2e2341e293aacc127fd66"},{"type":"text","text":"那试试：\n\n```\nopenclaw agents bindings\n```\n\n或者：\n```\nopenclaw bindings\n```\n\n看看帮助里 bindings 是怎么用的？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":109,"output":178,"cacheRead":59388,"cacheWrite":1054,"totalTokens":60729,"cost":{"input":0.000032699999999999995,"output":0.0002136,"cacheRead":0.00356328,"cacheWrite":0.00039525,"total":0.00420483}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775057815546,"responseId":"061c6e98af363b0aead476972079a31a"}}
