{"type":"message","id":"1b5f911f","parentId":"f9d2bb3d","timestamp":"2026-04-01T16:05:49.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"你是后台的 tts选品agent 吗\" which means \"Are you the tts selection expert agent in the backend?\"\n\nSo they're asking if I'm the tts agent. Based on the conversation context, yes I am - I'm running in the tts agent workspace, and the routing shows \"agent=tts:feishu:direct:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\" which confirms I'm the tts agent.\n\nThe user wants to know if I'm the tts (TTS-选品专家) agent. Yes I am.","thinkingSignature":"d9b9c1e4a0dcb0bfe0a9f0c8219e7c21e2b130f465f52dbb88c46509746a5a13"},{"type":"text","text":"对，我目前是 **TTS-选品专家** agent（tts），运行在 `~/.openclaw/workspace-selector`。\n\n不过刚才我们配置完了：\n- ✅ KIIT 账号已添加到 `channels.feishu.accounts`\n- ✅ main agent 已绑定到 `feishu accountId=kiit`\n- ✅ tts agent 仍然绑定到 `feishu accountId=tts`\n\n你重启 OpenClaw 之后，KIIT 应该就能绑定到 main agent 了。你试试从 KIIT 发一条消息，看看是不是 main agent 在回复你？\n\n如果 KIIT 还是连接到 tts agent，说明 KIIT 的 WebSocket 连接可能需要重新建立。你可以尝试重启 OpenClaw 或者重新链接 KIIT 机器人。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":140,"output":286,"cacheRead":61433,"cacheWrite":664,"totalTokens":62523,"cost":{"input":0.000042,"output":0.0003432,"cacheRead":0.0036859799999999997,"cacheWrite":0.000249,"total":0.00432018}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775059540163,"responseId":"061c7554cdaec653428131d549bf6aac"}}
